name: Hand painted brooch #4
description:
Brooches painted by children, teens and young adults from the 'People with special needs' program in Thailand. By purchasing this brooch you are helping to fund this wonderful program that enriches the lives of so many people.

* These brooches are made using non-toxic water based acrylics.
* Measures 5.5cm x 5.5cm

A bit about the People with special needs program:
'We are called "People with Special Needs" and you will understand our specialty when you get to know us. Though we do not see the word as others, we can make beautiful things, and these are the artworks that we have produced with our teachers and friends. While we are drawing, and sculpting, some of our friends are running around, playing. Some of us can sit still for quite a while, but it's our joyful time together and look, some paintings are so calm, some look confused, some give you the feel of speed. So many feelings, and this is how we are unique from others.

name: Cork wallet - colour flecked
description:
Cork wallet with colour flecks, made using high quality thin cork shavings taken directly from the cork oak tree.
Cork is a sustainable and environmentally friendly material.

This wallet is soft to the touch, flexible, waterproof and easily cleaned.
It is as durable as leather and as flexible as fabric.

Designed and made in Thailand

*11.5 x 9.2cm
*6 card slots (can fit more than 1 card in each slot)
*Hidden slots behind card slot
*Divided notes section giving you double the space for notes and receipts
*Sim card holder
